() Tj
T* (Trade-offs:) Tj
T* (- Extra memory for heaps and occupied set.) Tj
T* (- Lazy deletion may temporarily store stale heap entries; periodically compacting heaps can) Tj
T* (control growth.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (7. Implementation) Tj
T* (Language: Python 3) Tj
T* (Core file:) Tj
T* (- parking_system.py with:) Tj
T* (  - ParkingSpot dataclass) Tj
T* (  - CampusParkingIndex class) Tj
T* (  - operations: occupy, release, get_available_spots) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (8. Sample Input and Output \(Minimum 5 sets\)) Tj
T* (Set 1) Tj
T* (Input : area=North, k=2) Tj
T* (Output: [N-101, N-103]) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Set 2) Tj
T* (Input : occupy\(N-101\), area=North, k=2) Tj
T* (Output: [N-103, N-102]) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Set 3) Tj
T* (Input : occupy\(N-103\), area=North, k=3) Tj
T* (Output: [N-102]) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Set 4) Tj
T* (Input : release\(N-101\), area=North, k=2) Tj
T* (Output: [N-101, N-102]) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Set 5) Tj
T* (Input : area=Central, k=5) Tj
T* (Output: [C-201, C-202]) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (9. Time and Space Complexity Analysis) Tj
T* (Let n be total spots, and n_a be spots in requested area.) Tj
T* (- Build index: O\(n log n_a*\) total insertion cost across heaps \(practically O\(n log n\)) Tj
T* (worst-case single area\)) Tj
T* (- occupy: O\(1\)) Tj
T* (- release: O\(log n_a\)) Tj
T* (- get_available_spots\(area, k\): O\(\(k + s\) log n_a\), where s is count of stale popped entries) Tj
T* (Best case query:) Tj
T* (- First heap entries are valid -> O\(k log n_a\); for k=1 this is near O\(1\) practical latency) Tj
T* (Space:) Tj
T* (- O\(n\) for spot map + area heaps + occupied set) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (10. Conclusion) Tj
